<center><table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>
<center><strong>Ice Comet</strong></center>
</font></td></tr>
</table></center>
<table width=70%>
<tr><td>Mana:</td>
<td>400</td></tr>
<tr><td>Skill:</td>
<td>Evocation</td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top>
Classes:</td>
<td>
<a href="/spells/wizard.shtml">
Wizard</a>
 (49)<BR>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>Buyable:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Researchable:</td><td>
Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>Drops from MOB:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Cast Time:</td>
<td>6.30 seconds</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><br></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>Description:</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
Deals up to 1120 damage to target.<BR>
<BR>
Obtained through the <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/quests/ice_comet_quest.shtml">Ice Comet Quest</a>.</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
<BR>1 tick = 6 seconds<BR>
When a range of effects are given, it usually means that the effect becomes more potent as the caster increases in levels.
</td></tr>
</table>
