<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Seems that you are confused my friend about the Necro / Shaman spells. Where as Necros and Shaman seem to specialize in diseases of sorts (better know as a DOT}, Wizards are very efficient at Direct Damage Magic. Thus a wizard will get an immediate 1200 damage for a rather efficient 400 mana. Hope that answers your questions or confusion.<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
